text: Nicola Cassidy (born 9 December 1955) is an Irish equestrian. She competed in the team eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Irish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Ireland Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Dublin (city)
